      "content": "I see. So if there's no real scientific consensus on the danger, it sounds like some of the calls for heavy regulation might be premature or even counterproductive. If we move too slow because of these hypothetical risks, aren't we just letting other players (or even adversarial nations) pull ahead while we're stuck in red tape?",
